latestIgtvVideos.title: 3 UNUSUAL YET PRETTY SIMPLE WAYS OF WEARING LINER 🌸🤩

latestPosts.caption:
Did we just tick off the biggest thing on our bucket list that too on Christmas Eve? 🥹🥹🥹🥹
OMGGGG, I cannot believe I’m writing this. WE SAW THE BEST BEST BEST AURORA SHOW! After 1 complete flop show of Aurora chasing tour, 3 nights of 100% cloud coverage with no show at all, 2 nights of very faint green lights in the sky, WE FINALLY FINALLY chased & caught them! We witnessed the best AURORA SHOW that we could possibly see! 😭😭😭

We were not even supposed to be there on this night, but somehow it all just aligned! Infact, the weather forecast wasn’t great either, barely any chances of seeing the lights but we knew it was going to be something that night!!!! Because the whole day was the most clear and the brightest day we saw in the past 10 days & it happened! Forecast sucked but it happened. 

WE SAW THE AURORAS DANCING above us, in greens and proper reds or pink or whatever you wanna call it. Lady Aurora was dancing & how! And it went on for 1.5 hours straight, WHAAAAT!!!! 
No jokes, 1.5 hour straight, we didn’t step inside the van for even a minute because it just kept happening & changing and getting fainter & then getting brighter than ever. 1 dance after the other, 1 explosion after the other, 1 line to 2 lines to 3 lines to crazy shapes and forms, it just didn’t stop for 90 minutes!!!

It was -26 degrees outside, but we could feel nothing but the magic, the excitement, didn’t care about being in the cold for 2 hours, about the fingers & feet going all numb. Nothing mattered, except for what was happening in the sky. Just nothing else mattered.

I mean, I have no right way or words to describe this. I’m just typing and typing and this is just unfiltered emotions coming out right now. 

IT WAS CRAZY! MAGICAL! MADNESS! 

Cannot believe it happened. Still cannot fully process that it happened & in the most magical way possible. THANK YOU GOD, for this day, for this moment, for this life ✨🧿🙏🏻

Don’t know if she’s more beautiful or Swiss 🇨🇭😍

Adulting I guess? 🫠
Turned 29, spent my day completely disconnected with the outer world, tuned in just to find out, I am really not sure of anything, hahah!
There’s this immense pressure on a man (humans in general) when coming close to thirtees, to have it all “figured out!”
but honestly, I don’t really know where life is headed, but well, I am just here, only trying to live every bit of it! Cherish every bit of it!
Grateful for every bit of it, got to spend the day with only nature and greenery all around & as far as I could see! Bus aur kya hi chahiye? 🍃 
Thank you so much for all your lovely messages & blessings!
